By Lisa Shock on Saturday, December 30, 2000 - 08:41 pm:

Having spent years working for a company that sold it, I know that there were at least 4 versions of the CD pressed. (I don't own any of them.) It's a popular program that's been around since before CD drives were in computers, and it's been through a few facelifts.
